### MDF Test File - All Input Types

# Text Inputs:
Name: [Enter your name]
Email: [your@email.com]{email}
Phone: [123-456-7890]{tel}

# Required Text Inputs:
Full Name: [First and Last Name]*

# Number Inputs:
Number of participants: [5]
Quantity: [3;1..5]
Items: [;0..10]
Price: [5.0]
Precision: [3.14;0..10]

# Text Inputs (Should NOT be treated as number)
Text with semicolon: [abc;1..5]

Text with dots: [5.0]

Text with two dots: [1..10]

Text placeholder: [Enter your name]

Text with range-like: [1 to 10]

# Date Inputs:
Event Date: [DD/MM/YYYY]
Birth Date: [DD/MM/YYYY;1979-01-01..1979-12-31]

# Textarea:
Description: [Multi-line text...]

# Dropdown Select:
Number of participants: [Please select ▼; 1 person, 2 people, 3 people]

# Radio Buttons:
Gender: [( ) Male, ( ) Female, (x) Other]

# Checkboxes:
Interests: [[x] Sports, [ ] Music, [ ] Reading]

# Toggle Switch:
Subscribe to newsletter: [Enable notifications: ON/OFF]

# Markdown Text (Non-Input):
